column2: Match Group Inc., IAC/InterActivecorp (IAC), through its portfolio companies provides dating products available globally. The Companyâ€™s portfolio of brands includes Tinder, Match, Meetic, OkCupid, Hinge, Pairs, PlentyOfFish, and OurTime, and other brands designed for users' likelihood to find a meaningful connection. Through its portfolio companies and their brands, the Company provide tailored products and enables connections across the spectrum of age, gender and dating goals. Its products are available in over 40 languages to users all over the world.
